data.description: STUNNING CUL-DE-SAC LOT! NO HOA! Supersize Lot! Room for RV and/or toys!  You will be impressed with this impeccable 5 bedroom, 2 bathroom & Fireplace block home. Let the entryway lead you to an open floor plan showcasing the spacious living room & formal dining room with patio views. Then make your way to an updated kitchen with granite counter tops, breakfast bar, new stainless steel appliances, modern cabinets & frosted glass door walk-in pantry. The cozy family room enjoys a block wood-burning fireplace. The opposite wing of the home includes a large master bedroom, large master bathroom with private exit door & large closet. The backyard has the most charming patio with all new tile. The covered RV parking/workshop structure will impress you beyond belief!
